{"tid":304821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.1遊行】香港獨立集會    近百名警員戒備","createTime":"2017-07-01T07:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T11:43:14.000Z","uid":48093,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"666e596efc2bb8099c0ab5fc785240088873bc52","tid":304821,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170701/large/1498894462_13aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170701%2Flarge%2F1498894462_13aa.jpg&h=d8b7678e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行尚未開始，支持香港獨立的鄭俠於鵝頸橋豎起香港獨立旗幟，有十數名市民參與集會，及後亦有多名身穿印有香港民族陣線字樣衣服的市民參與集會，多名警察隨即介入了解，現場已有近百警員戒備。鄭俠指昨晚於網上發起集會，未能預計參與人數，但多強調每個支持港獨的市民有權利參與集會。<br />\n<br />\n同樣支持港獨的香港民族黨陳浩天昨亦於尖沙咀發起集會，卻遭警阻撓。鄭指「港共最驚就係港獨，一定要堅持」。<br />\n多個藍絲組織稍後亦會於鵝頸橋集會，鄭指已做好「畀人打嘅準備」。"},{"pid":"56f8e6c5f45e482fa3567a1d23dbe227b70bd5f5","tid":304821,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a340e13b113ea110d56d03ca5aa40de48f441b","tid":304821,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d803c66c8b6270073fbc3493d812b6594c2a6","tid":304821,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01662107c8170797ff07bf79208e5380c75ec45","tid":304821,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c522dcc1ef54f1f3d85109ea480ae27317133e85","tid"